thread.title_full: Dinky Dog Club reviewed by Charisma Phillips

author: Charisma Phillips
title: Charisma Phillips
text: I loved the clothes I purchased and my Khloe loved the treats that was sent as a thank you gift. I'm falling in love with the company. Fast shipping is a big plus. Everything is nice, the packaging, wrapping, discount card that is sent. I had a awesome experience. Much love
